New SC documentation system, work in progress
=============================================

The markup language parser is in ScDoc.sc, copy or symlink this to your Extensions folder.
Try it like this:

p = ScDocParser.new
p.parse("/home/lijon/Coding/ScDoc/test.sch")
p.dump

